				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Greetings,
<br />

<br />
   The way I describe Mend Companion is as an instant, no target, mana free, Healing Of Sorsha.   Problem is MC by itself has a 36 minute refresh.   Hastend Mending though, goes a very long way to making it very useful.
<br />

<br />
   Hastened Mending 1 gives refresh of 26 minutes.  Still too long to really be worth while IMO
<br />

<br />
   Hastened Mending 2 gives a refresh of ~16 minutes.  Still not really worth it to me.
<br />

<br />
   Hastened Mending 3 gives a refresh of 9 minutes.  Ooooh...  Daddy likes.
<br />

<br />
   With Hastened mending 3, I describe it as an instant, no target, mana free, Healing Of Sorsha every 9 minutes.  <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="Wink" border="0" /><br />_________________<br /><ul><li><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=67241">Elder Kaatt</a>, Sixty-Five Year Old Khati Sha Feral Lord of Xev.<li><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=337255">Investigator Aaeorn</a>, Fifty-Third Circle Redeemed Thief Catcher of Xev.<li><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=362220">Aaeorm</a>, Enchantement Technician of the Fortieth Tier of Xev.<li>Proud member of <A HREF="http://www.devotionguild.com">Devotion</a></ul></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
